Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, recoll
Description: Find documents using full-text search
 Recall lets you search your document library using a powerful query language.
 Searches results appear instantly as you type, and a context menu entry
 (contractor) offers you to quickly search any folder from Files.
